OL,3,EQ.A.D.GPC``````````````````````````````
OL,4,G                                       
OL,5,BWe know what you're wondering, and the 
OL,6,Banswer is "Quintessential Art of       
OL,7,BDestruction". MDK? KKND? Will this     
OL,8,Bnightmare never end?                   
OL,10,FDespite its modest 3D graphics engine, 
OL,11,FQ.A.D. is a real return to the         
OL,12,Fprinciples of gaming. It plays very    
OL,13,Fmuch like an old 8-bit computer title: 
OL,14,FDefender, or something like that.      
OL,16,BYou see, you fly around in a spaceship 
OL,17,Bthing, collecting "pods", filling them 
OL,18,Bup with hostages, and depositing the   
OL,19,Bhostages in your base. Got that?       
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````1/8``
OL,21, B    News stuffF171B"E" is forF173     
OL,22,B]MD     TURNER THE EYEBALL p196        
OL,24,AReviews  BHot topic  CTV  FGo Green    
PN,17202
SC,0002
FL,173,174,110,160,1ff,170
OL,1,R{%|l4|h4sh<|h444Qo?'ss+o$pp  
OL,2,Rj5s1oz%jwsjk5Q #//#xt#o/a~?$
OL,3,EQ.A.D.GPC``````````````````````````````
OL,5,BThough Q.A.D. makes a few nods towards 
OL,6,Bthe Nineties, notably in the           
OL,7,Bpresentation, and the reliance on      
OL,8,Bpower-ups to spice up the action, at   
OL,9,Bits heart is a real retro trip.        
OL,11,FCalling a game "Defender in 3D" has    
OL,12,Fbeen done before, but there's very     
OL,13,Flittle other description that fits     
OL,14,FQ.A.D. As crusty old fogies, we enjoyed
OL,15,Fevery minute of it.                    
OL,17,BIt might be a little simplistic for    
OL,18,Bsome, but there's little here to offend
OL,19,Byour tongue.                           
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````2/8``
