OL,3,EOVERBLOODGPlayStation``````````````````
OL,4,BIt'd be easy to sum up Overblood in a  
OL,5,Bsingle sentence, so we will: a sci-fi  
OL,6,BResident Evil with less shooting.      
OL,8,FOverblood begins with you waking from a
OL,9,Fcryogenically-induced sleep. You don't 
OL,10,Fknow who you are. You don't where you  
OL,11,Fare. You probably don't even know what 
OL,12,FThe Flintstones is.                    
OL,14,BIt becomes clear fairly early on that  
OL,15,Byou're trapped in an underground       
OL,16,Binstallation which has been torn       
OL,17,Basunder by some sort of catastrophe.   
OL,18,BThe few staff that remain have been    
OL,19,Btransformed into horrid zombie guys.   
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````4/8``
