OL,24,AReviews  BHot topic  CTV  FGo Green    
PN,17205
SC,0005
FL,173,174,110,160,1ff,170
OL,1,R{%|l4|h4sh<|h444Qo?'ss+o$pp  
OL,2,Rj5s1oz%jwsjk5Q #//#xt#o/a~?$
OL,3,EOVERBLOODGPlayStation``````````````````
OL,5,BThough essentially a third-person      
OL,6,Bperspective adventure game, there's    
OL,7,Balso the option to play Overblood from 
OL,8,Ba first-person perspective. The full-  
OL,9,Bpolygon graphics engine makes for some 
OL,10,Bsplendid views of the action.          
OL,12,FDuring the game you'll meet up with    
OL,13,Fother characters, who'll join your     
OL,14,Fteam. You'll be able to swap between   
OL,15,Fthe different members - essential if   
OL,16,Fyou have to split up.                  
OL,18,BSo, perhaps it isn't a complete        
OL,19,BResident Evil clone...                 
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````5/8``
OL,21, BTeen for twoF140BWitness the indexF100
OL,22,B]MDBAMBER IN "WHOLEWHEAT" SHOCK p152   
OL,24,AReviews  BHot topic  CTV  FGo Green    
PN,17206
SC,0006
FL,173,174,110,160,1ff,170
OL,1,R{%|l4|h4sh<|h444Qo?'ss+o$pp  
OL,2,Rj5s1oz%jwsjk5Q #//#xt#o/a~?$
OL,3,EOVERBLOODGPlayStation``````````````````
OL,5,BFor most of Overblood you'll be        
OL,6,Bexploring and problem-solving. It's a  
OL,7,Bfairly linear quest, but your          
OL,8,Benvironment is superbly designed and   
OL,9,Batmospheric.                           
OL,11,FSound gets a special mention. The      
OL,12,Feffects are eerie, while the speech -  
OL,13,Falthough not perfect - is light years  
OL,14,Fahead of Resident Evil (Though "Peepo" 
OL,15,Fthe robot's death scene is a comedy    
OL,16,Fclassic in league with RE's "Master of 
OL,17,FUnlocking" dialogue).                  
OL,19,BIt's generally well-acted and logical. 
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````6/8``
OL,21, B    News stuffF171B"E" is forF173     
OL,22,B]MD     TURNER THE EYEBALL p196        
OL,24,AReviews  BHot topic  CTV  FGo Green    
PN,17207
SC,0007
FL,173,174,110,160,1ff,170
OL,1,R{%|l4|h4sh<|h444Qo?'ss+o$pp  
OL,2,Rj5s1oz%jwsjk5Q #//#xt#o/a~?$
OL,3,EOVERBLOODGPlayStation``````````````````
OL,5,BPerhaps the reason why we found        
OL,6,BOverblood so gripping was its plot.    
OL,8,FYou don't expect an adventure of this  
OL,9,Fnature to have much in the way of      
OL,10,Fstoryline - just a series of set-piece 
OL,11,Fpuzzles and surprises.                 
OL,13,BOverblood, however, twists and turns   
OL,14,Blike the best Hollywood movie.         
OL,15,BAdmittedly, it's hardly, Wayne's World 
OL,16,B2, but it's pretty neat nonetheless.   
OL,18,FMuch better than you'd expect it to be.
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````7/8``
